The paper focuses on data augmentation techniques for deep learning models, specifically in the context of image classification and object detection. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of learned augmentation strategies, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing (cs.CL) and neural networks (cs.NE) in passing, although these are not the main focus of the paper. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.LG, followed by cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.NE.
